Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.90,0:23:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.42,0:23:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.16,0:23:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现任店主是我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.25,0:23:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…
